    Settings
    --------

Settings

    The {{{../api/Gldapo.getSettings()}settings object}} holds some global values which are used as default values.

    The available settings are ...

*--*--*--*--*
|| Name || Type || Default || Description 
*--*--*--*--*
| pageSize | Integer | 500 | The default page size to use for searches where no page size is specified
*--*--*--*--*